Property management  
Manual reservations  
Dashboard

Phase 2

Guest CRM  
Reservation editing  
Operational dashboard

Phase 3

Services  
Cleaning workflow  
Booking integration

Phase 4

Admin panel  
Billing  
Multi-user teams

---

# 15. Development Workflow

The project uses an AI-assisted workflow.

Roles:

ChatGPT
Architecture and product design

Cursor + Codex
Code generation

Claude
Secondary AI coding assistant

GitHub
Version control

